object.customQuery:
select count(*) as pilot_batch_count, source_system_code from metal.batch_load_summary_poc
where source_system_code = 'ADM'  and batch_id =1
group by source_system_code

attributes.name: Download S3 Files In Multiple Parts

object.customQuery:
select * from (
select  source_system_code, MAX(recent_b_query.batch_id) as latest_batch, recent_b_query.target_table_name, recent_b_query.recent_b_status
from (
select batch_id, target_table_name, batch_status,source_system_code, last_value(batch_status) over(partition by batch_id, target_table_name order by batch_status asc rows between unbounded preceding and unbounded following) as recent_b_status
from (select * from metal.batch_load_summary_poc
where source_system_code = 'ADM' and batch_status in ('SUCCESS', 'FAILED', 'Inprogress') --and  batch_id !=1
)
order by batch_id) recent_b_query
group by batch_id,target_table_name, recent_b_status, source_system_code
order by batch_id desc ,target_table_name, recent_b_status
)
where latest_batch = (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(batch_id), 1) AS batch_id
  FROM metal.batch_load_summary_poc)

object.customQuery:
select  count(*) as recent_batch_count, 'ADM' as source_system_id from (
select  source_system_code, MAX(recent_b_query.batch_id) as latest_batch, recent_b_query.target_table_name, recent_b_query.recent_b_status
from (
select batch_id, target_table_name, batch_status,source_system_code, last_value(batch_status) over(partition by batch_id, target_table_name order by batch_status asc rows between unbounded preceding and unbounded following) as recent_b_status
from (select * from metal.batch_load_summary_poc
where source_system_code = 'ADM' and batch_status in ('SUCCESS', 'FAILED', 'Inprogress') and  batch_id !=1)
order by batch_id) recent_b_query
group by batch_id,target_table_name, recent_b_status, source_system_code
order by batch_id desc ,target_table_name, recent_b_status
)
where latest_batch = (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(batch_id), 1) AS batch_id
  FROM metal.batch_load_summary_poc)
